Template: orkllm/lib_path
Type: string
Default: /usr/lib/librkllmrt.so
Description: Path to librkllmrt.so (Rockchip RKLLM runtime library):
 Enter the full path to the Rockchip RKLLM runtime shared library.
 This library is distributed with the official Rockchip RKLLM SDK and
 is typically installed at /usr/lib/librkllmrt.so.
 .
 If the library is not yet installed, you can leave this as the default
 and update ORKLLM_LIB_PATH in /etc/orkllm/orkllm.conf later.
